data.description: ONE ACRE OF NON DEED RESTRICTED freedom.   NEW ROOF (late 2018), New Exterior Paint (2019), A/C 2014.  4 CAR GARAGE.  3 BD, 3 Full Bath.  This house is being sold as part of a trust and was custom built by the original owner.   This house has a beautiful INDOOR POOL in a huge room measuring 53X21.  Indoor pool area has a full bath. Every room that adjoins the pool has sliding doors leading to it (4 sets of sliders leading to the pool area).  Separate 2 car workshop/garage with plenty of working space inside.   The owner had converted the garage into living space (not permitted) so it is under-air and has sliding glass doors on the outside.   This garage still has it's garage door so you can still use it for it's original purpose of a 2 car garage.   Total 4 car garages.  The floors are polished concrete.   Laundry room has a sink and overhead cabinets.    All appliances sell with the house.  All room measurements are believed to be correct but should be verified by buyers and buyer's agent.  Call today for a private preview.  Walk thru this house with our VIRTUAL TOUR attached.
